{"tid":2275871,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃竹坑站上蓋地盤起火 濃煙攻入警察學院","createTime":"2020-11-07T13:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T17:42:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":715,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"9be6b61515c7d28e0f52bbcdcc29258a5b7e4d8b","tid":2275871,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sH6K3CrHZou09eued1N3lH3WD1c=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DZMIYDA6JZDB3LF6UCZD4XD3CE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsH6K3CrHZou09eued1N3lH3WD1c%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDZMIYDA6JZDB3LF6UCZD4XD3CE.jpg&h=8e524e32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港仔發生火警。傍晚6時許，黃竹坑南朗山道23號一地盤突然起火，冒出陣陣濃煙，消防接報到場開喉灌救，大約至晚上7時將火救熄，事件中無人受傷，初步調查估計是建築材料被燃點而起火。據知現場為黃竹坑站上蓋第一期地盤，火警發生期間大量濃煙湧入警察學院及旁邊的宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5K-TRUhonYmjKnCr2f0gDArYVWQ=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TEU5JHB5HBGEFNXZ4AHHECE3OY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5K-TRUhonYmjKnCr2f0gDArYVWQ%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTEU5JHB5HBGEFNXZ4AHHECE3OY.jpg&h=1c425a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201107/W6WSNDZSTJBZ5IP7WFCSRW7A44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201107%2FW6WSNDZSTJBZ5IP7WFCSRW7A44%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=de9a4b9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201107%2FW6WSNDZSTJBZ5IP7WFCSRW7A44%2F&h=5d3e0125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.co